results.title: Live. Love. Laugh. Silver Hand-Made Bracelet
results.description: This bracelet speaks a simple, yet important message. LIVE life to its fullest, LOVE deeply and LAUGH often. This exquisite piece is 100% handmade (other than the lobster clasp). Each disc was hand-cut and hand-stamped and the jump rings are hand cut and soldered closed for additional security. The font has an antique look, resembling the font generated by typewriters (remember those???). The bracelet is 7” long and makes a great everyday piece that looks amazing layered as well! Makes a great gift for a special loved one, a teacher, a friend or for yourself. I wear mine all the time to reminder me to live fully, love deeply and laugh often.

results.title: Modern Charm Bracelet - Hand Stamped Twisted Cord with Onyx and Pearl - Sterling Silver Charms
results.description:
Charm bracelet - Live Laugh Love....in Sterling Silver

I love this so much I made one for me right away!!

A customer asked me for a thicker cord - so I made this cord with 8 strands of my secret cord.  It is remarkably comfortable to wear.  You never have to take it off!  It is totally waterproof.  It has a sturdy sterling lobster claw clasp.

This one says Live, Laugh, Love --- the two last pictures say Let It Be, Ride The Wave and All Is Well.  You can fit up to 14-15 characters around each ring.  

This one comes with three discs, one cross charm (you may have a heart/additional stamped charm instead - or convo me with a request for a charm you would like!) - on the other side is a gorgeous creamy pearl and a faceted black onyx bead.  You may have crystals (like birthstones) or any other color beads - I have many different color corals and stones.

You can have childrens names and birthstones - or anything you like!

It will come to you ready for gift giving in a totally reusable and recyclable and really cute gift tin!
materials: awl reel heavy leather lacing cord
